Title: Scroll down, insert blank line?
Type: Bug
Units_of_Work: 1000
--
Current scroll down doesn't create a new line when scrolling. Instead it just goes into the scrollback if there are lines. Is this correct? Empirical evidence suggests that most terminal emulators create a new blank line when scrolling down.